As a user I can search a deal from where I am
To only show the relevant deals

As a user I can see all deals
To get a look at what I want

As a user I can log-in/sign-up
To be able to do more

As a user I can see weekly deals
To see deals in the future

As a user I can save deals to my deals
To be able to remember future deals

As a user I can see details about a deal
To know more about it

As a user I can filter the deals
To narrow the search down

As a user I can view my profile and my deals
To keep track of them
